ğŸ“‹ Pull Request Process
1.	Before You Start
o	Check existing issues and PRs
o	Open an issue to discuss major changes
o	Ensure your fork is up to date
2.	Making Changes
o	Create a descriptive branch name (feature_name/document_generator, fix/web-layout)
o	Write clear, concise commit messages
o	Keep commits focused and atomic
3.	Submitting PR
o	Fill out the PR template completely
o	Link to relevant issues
o	Add screenshots for UI changes
o	Request review from maintainers
