Git Commit Messages
â€¢	Use present tense ("Add feature" not "Added feature")
â€¢	Use imperative mood ("Move cursor to..." not "Moves cursor to...")
â€¢	Limit first line to 72 characters
â€¢	Reference issues and PRs when applicable
